    <entry>
      <title type="html">hadoop 환경 설치 (1)</title>
      <link href="https://kilhyeonjun.github.io/hadoop-base-1" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="hadoop 환경 설치 (1)" />
      <published>2021-09-14T20:50:00+00:00</published>
      <updated>2021-09-14T20:50:00+00:00</updated>
      <id>https://kilhyeonjun.github.io/hadoop-base-1</id>
      <content type="html" xml:base="https://kilhyeonjun.github.io/hadoop-base-1">&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;table-of-contents-list&quot;&gt;hadoop 개념정리&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;table-of-contents-list&quot;&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;./hadoop-base-1&quot;&gt;하둡 1.hadoop 환경 설치 (1)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;./hadoop-base-2&quot;&gt;하둡 2.hadoop 환경 설치 (2)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;본 게시물은 윈도우 환경에서 진행하였습니다.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h1 id=&quot;virtualbox-설치&quot;&gt;VirtualBox 설치&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;assets/built/images/hadoop/vbdown.PNG&quot; alt=&quot;img&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.virtualbox.org/wiki/Downloads&quot;&gt;다운로드&lt;/a&gt; 를 클릭하여 해당 페이지로 이동&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Windows hosts 클릭 후 exe 파일 설치&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;머신 - 새로만들기&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;우분투를 설치 할 것이기 때문에&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;종류 Linux&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;버전 Ubuntu(64bit)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

